{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CalDAV","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/CalDAV","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>CalDAV（Calendaring extensions to <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/WebDAV\">WebDAV</a>）は、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/IETF\">IETF</a> によって標準化された<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">プロトコル</a>であり、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Server\">サーバー</a>からカレンダーデータにリモートアクセスするために使用されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"より詳しく知る","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia 上の <a title=\"CalDAV\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/CalDAV\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CalDAV</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technical_reference","title":"技術文書","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4791\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 4791: Calendaring extensions to WebDAV (CalDAV)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6638\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 6638: Scheduling Extensions to CalDAV</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"より詳しく知る","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"CalDAV（Calendaring extensions to WebDAV）は、IETF によって標準化されたプロトコルであり、サーバーからカレンダーデータにリモートアクセスするために使用されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CalDAV","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"CalDAV","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CalDAV","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CalDAV","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/caldav","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/caldav/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parent